channel.title: Well Lived Negroes
channel.itunes:subtitle: A group of friends discussing the well-lived lifestyle.
channel.itunes:author: Colin Williams, Kamal Barney, and Jason Banks
channel.itunes:summary: Well Lived Negroes is a show about living a life well. Each week we dive into any subject known to man and talk about it as much as we can. Look for our podcast in the Podcasts app or in the iTunes Store.
